{"tid":531094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【立會補選】陳玉娥捲土重來　正式報名再戰新東","createTime":"2018-01-16T12:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T02:49:51.000Z","uid":145488,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"62aa1789dfd77607ab8d5289acdfd5cfa0ae7b4c","tid":531094,"uid":145488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:29:16.000Z","msg":"立法會補選提名期今日（16日）展開，2016年參加立法會新界東直選、在選舉論壇爆出「CY就係太完美」的「娥姐」陳玉娥捲土重來，今日正式報名參加新界東補選。<br />\n<br />\n立法會補選提名期今日（16日）展開，至本月29日結束。其中2016年參加立法會新界東直選的「娥姐」陳玉娥，今日正式報名出戰新界東補選。<br />\n<br />\n報稱是公司董事、政治聯繫為「獨立無黨派候選人」的陳玉娥前年參選時，在選舉論壇爆出「CY就係太完美」、「我諗佢見到我會即刻縮」等金句而聲名大噪，還遭網民惡搞他與公民黨黨魁楊岳橋爆出「娥頸橋之戀」，為網民津津樂道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/150250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F150250&d=1XqBj0AsuG9BAg1bToNApcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=cb9de373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/150250</a>"},{"pid":"27c3770b0c363fb2da627b31fc2a3548cb1d5f3e","tid":531094,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:29:47.000Z","msg":"我情願投陳國強"},{"pid":"c4642fbd97069f2d95dbd913adfb93efc4717bfe","tid":531094,"uid":95397,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"終極痴線婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9302d4a45307eeacdce6261158701f18359e8dc","tid":531094,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又黎"},{"pid":"9af6384a1ecba20d85a79a31e7c072395f0a1725","tid":531094,"uid":3454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"又諗起澳門個扎鐵侯選人"},{"pid":"a383c62cce725adeef522cabcd6bf76cf1b3a7f6","tid":531094,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"支持娥姐"},{"pid":"b026115878d7bec147ebd5aeb82006b1c6ab0a9b","tid":5